	** Fixes part of bug #546892

	* em-folder-browser.c:
	* em-format-html-display.c:
	* mail-send-recv.c:
	* message-tag-followup.c:
	Prefer gtk_image_new_from_icon_name() over e_icon_factory_get_image().

	* mail-send-recv.c:
	* message-tag-followup.c:
	Prefer gtk_window_set_icon_name() over gtk_window_set_icon_list().

