2006-08-09  Srinivasa Ragavan  <sragavan@novell.com>

	** Fix for bug #350411 #350476
	
	* em-mailer-prefs.c (notify_sound_changed): When prefs comes up,
	nothing is set in FILE chooser, so it returns NULL and bypass it.
