	(em_format_default_headers): loop through everything.

2004-05-14  Jeffrey Stedfast  <fejj@novell.com>

	* em-popup.h: s/RESEND/EDIT/

	* em-popup.c (em_popup_target_new_select): s/RESEND/EDIT/

	* em-folder-view.c: s/RESEND/EDIT/
